Load-shedding will continue to be implemented at stage 3 until midnight, no longer stage 4, Eskom said on Wednesday. The overnight load-shedding at stage 2 will be reduced to stage 1 from midnight to 5am. On Thursday, stage 3 load-shedding will be implemented between 5am and 4pm, before moving up to stage 4 from 4pm to midnight. TimesLIVE 